Description:
Welcome to a new era of proactive cybersecurity. We look at how Google's "Big Sleep" AI made history by discovering a critical SQLite vulnerability and helping patch it before it could be exploited. This marks a first for AI-powered defense, stopping a threat before it even begins.

#Google #AI #Cybersecurity
